IGC sells Malaysian hotel investment interest
Wednesday, 5 Apr 2017 06:00am EDT 
India Globalization Capital Inc  : IGC sells Malaysian hotel investment interest . Has sold its ten percent holding in Brilliant Hallmark for a consideration of four million shares of co .Company does not expect to record a gain or loss from this transaction. 
			
