India Globalization Capital Raises $600 Thousand in Direct Equity Investment
Thursday, 25 Feb 2016 09:36am EST 
India Globalization Capital, Inc:raised $600,000 in a private placement. 2,142,856 shares of newly issued common stock were sold at yesterday's closing price of $0.28 per share.After fees and expenses, the net proceeds to IGC are approximately $590,000.The net proceeds from the offering are for working capital. The offering closed on February 24, 2016, subject to customary closing conditions. 
			
